  schema:name "Formalizing Sign Theory: A Survey of Mathematical Approaches to Semiotics" ;
  schema:description "A survey of mathematical formalizations of semiotics — algebraic, functorial, topos-theoretic, and relational — assessing what each approach captures and where it falls short." ;
